    <item>
      <title>在英国，电动汽车的保险费用是燃油汽车的两倍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/uk-electric-car-insurance-costs-twice-as-much-as-gasoline-and-diesel-cover</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国司机必须为电动汽车支付两倍于内燃机车型的保险费用，这增加了转向零排放汽车的障碍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/uk-electric-car-insurance-costs-twice-as-much-as-gasoline-and-diesel-cover</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>保时捷投资者对超级跑车股票失去了对竞争对手法拉利的希望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/porsche-investors-lose-hope-of-a-supercar-stock-to-rival-ferrari</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当大众汽车公司 (Volkswagen AG) 于 2022 年底分拆保时捷公司 (Porsche AG) 时，投资界憧憬着能够与法拉利 (Ferrari) 竞争的超级跑车股票。这个梦想尚未成为现实，一些投资者怀疑它是否会成为现实。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/porsche-investors-lose-hope-of-a-supercar-stock-to-rival-ferrari</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着冲击消退，加拿大国家铁路维持盈利增长预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/cn-railway-cnr-stands-by-earnings-growth-forecast-as-shocks-subside</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大国家铁路公司 (Canadian National Railway Co.) 坚持未来几年两位数利润增长的预期，摆脱了 2023 年劳工冲突、谷物运输量低和经济低迷的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/cn-railway-cnr-stands-by-earnings-growth-forecast-as-shocks-subside</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 22:58:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
